CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 28, 1959, pg. 3 reads: "An Advantageous Move - Fred Foreman, one of Pittsburgh's outstanding chess players gets ready to post his knight onto an advantageous spot during his match against 11 members of the University of Pittsburgh chess team at Schenley Hall. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Fred Foreman playing against eleven members of the University of Pittsburgh Chess Club, in Schenley Hall, another version
